== Two Club Opening

{warning} _We do NOT play Kokish_

*Default response*
@ 2D = weak or waiting

*Natural responses*
@ 2H = natural positive, any suit-quality
@ 2NT = bal 8-10 (or 13{OrMore})
@ 3NT = bal 11-12

*Transfer responses*
{warning} #DO NOT USE#
@ 2S = one-loser red-suit
@ 3C = one-loser black-suit
@ 3D,3H,3S,4C = transfer to solid suit

